description:
Helle Version des Mediengestalter.info Boards (für Firefox 3.0.x)

Für mehr Übersichtlichkeit (Beitragshover):

table.forumline tr:hover td{
        background: #F6E8D9 !important;
} 

Für FF 3.1bx ergänzen:

::selection {
	background: #F6E8D9;
	color: #333;
	}
::-moz-selection {
	background: #F6E8D9;
	color: #333;
}

css:
@-moz-document domain(mediengestalter.info){

body
{ margin: 0 auto !important; width: 1000px !important; background: #e3e3e3 !important; }

span
{ color: #222222 }

.spacerow
{ background: #444 !important; }

th
{ background: #444444 !important; border: solid 0px !important; }

.forumline
{ background: white !important; }

.cat
{ background: none !important; }

.catleft
{ background: #eeeeee !important; }

.catbottom
{ background: #eeeeee !important; }

.cathead
{ background: #eeeeee !important; }


.footer
{ background: #cccccc !important; }

.navigation
{ background: none !important; }

a:link, a:visited
{ text-decoration: underline !important; }

a:hover
{ display: inline-block; background-color: #666; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none !important; }

a, .row1, .postbody, .postdetails, .gensmall, .genmed, .portal, .cattitle, .mainmenu
{ font: 11px, Arial, !important; line-height: 16px !important; color: #222222 !important; text-decoration: none !important; }

.row3{
  background: #f9f9f9 !important;
}

.quote{
  background: #fff !important;
}

.button, .post, select, .mainoption
{ background: #eeeeee !important; border: none !important }

}
